\newlabel{fig:validation_scatter}{{4}{15}{Standalone theory--surrogate scatter over the validation grid saved in \texttt {outputs/validation}. Calibration agreement is close, but held-out validation error is materially larger. The result supports internal consistency of the surrogate workflow after calibration, while also indicating residual model discrepancy outside the calibration subset}{figure.4}{}}
